{{Infobox power station | name = Alltwalis Wind Farm | name_official = Blaengwen Wind farm | image = | image_caption = | location_map = Wales | location_map_size = | location_map_caption = | coordinates = {{coord|51|58|24|N|04|15|03|W|type:landmark|display=inline,title}} | country = [[Wales]], [[United Kingdom]] | location = near [[Brechfa Forest]], [[Carmarthenshire]] | status = Operational | construction_began = November 2008 | commissioned = December 2009 | decommissioned = | cost = | owner = [[Statkraft]] | operator = | ps_units_operational = 10 x Siemens 2.3&nbsp;MW | ps_units_manu_model = [[Siemens Wind Power]] | wind_hub_height = | wind_rotor_diameter = | wind_rated_speed = | wind_farm_type = | wind_site_elevation = | wind_site_usage = | wind_offshore_depth = | wind_offshore_distance = | ps_electrical_capacity = 23&nbsp;MW | ps_electrical_cap_fac = | website = }} The '''Alltwalis Wind Farm''' is a [[wind farm]] near [[Brechfa Forest]] located to the north of the town of [[Carmarthen]] in [[Wales]].
The facility is composed of 10&nbsp;wind turbines with a combined installed capacity of 23 [[megawatts]]. The expected annual production of electricity is around 65&nbsp;[[gigawatt]] hours (GWh).<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.alltwaliswindfarm.co.uk/|title=Alltwalis Wind Farm|accessdate=4 December 2009}}</ref> The farm was built by [[Statkraft]]. Construction began in November 2008, and was completed in December 2009.
==Noise pollution== Residents of the area have reported severe problems with [[noise pollution]] from the wind farm leading to health problems for people living in the area.<ref name="carmarthenjournal">{{cite news|url=http://www.carmarthenjournal.co.uk/drugs/story-15419890-detail/story.html |title='We should not have to take drugs' | publisher=Carmarthen Journal |date=2012-03-07 |accessdate=2015-03-31}}</ref> Criticism has been levelled at Statkraft for not taking the residents' concerns seriously.<ref name="jonathanedwards">{{cite web|url=http://www.jonathanedwards.org.uk/calls-for-alltwalis-wind-farm-to-be-shut-down?lang=en |title=Calls for Alltwalis Wind Farm to be shut down | publisher=[[Jonathan Edwards (Welsh politician)|Jonathan Edwards]] |date=2010-07-07 |accessdate=2015-03-31}}</ref>
