The '''Brăila Power Station''' is a large [[thermal power plant]] located in [[Brăila]], having 7 generation groups, 2 of 3 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]], 1 of 210 MW, 2 of 25 MW, 1 of 50 MW and 1 of 330 MW having a total [[electricity]] generation capacity of 856 MW.<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20070702024037/http://www.energie-gratis.ro/termocentrale.php Cele mai mari termocentrale din Romania {{ro}}]</ref> The power plant also has another 210 MW unit but it is decommissioned.
Its two chimneys are 250 metres and 200 metres tall.

